        "question": "The area (in sq. units) of the region\n<br><br>{ (x, y) : 0 $$ \\le $$ y $$ \\le $$ x<sup>2</sup> + 1, 0 $$ \\le $$ y $$ \\le $$ x + 1,\n<br><br/> $${1 \\over 2}$$ $$ \\le $$ x $$ \\le $$ 2 } is :",
