        "difficulty": "Medium",
        "type": "SCQ",
        "question": "Consider a region R = {(x, y) $$ \\in $$ R : x<sup>2</sup> $$ \\le $$ y $$ \\le $$ 2x}.\nif a line y = $$\\alpha $$ divides the area of region R into\ntwo equal parts, then which of the following is\ntrue?",
