        "question": "If the area (in sq. units) bounded by the parabola y<sup>2</sup>\n = 4$$\\lambda $$x and the line y = $$\\lambda $$x, $$\\lambda $$ &gt; 0, is $${1 \\over 9}$$\n, then $$\\lambda $$ is equal to :",
