        "solution": "Required area\n<br><br><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1l91nf3yh/b4e886d1-7f41-4b72-ab7a-245bf94417c9/ef2e8480-47fb-11ed-8757-0f869593f41f/file-1l91nf3yi.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1l91nf3yh/b4e886d1-7f41-4b72-ab7a-245bf94417c9/ef2e8480-47fb-11ed-8757-0f869593f41f/file-1l91nf3yi.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2015 (Offline) Mathematics - Area Under The Curves Question 157 English Explanation\"><br>$$ = $$ Area of $$ABCD$$ $$-$$ $$ar$$ $$(ABOCD)$$\n<br><br 1=\"\" $$=\"\\int\\limits_{\" -=\"\" 2}^1=\"\" {{{y=\"\" +=\"\" 1}=\"\" \\over=\"\" 4}}=\"\" dy=\"\" \\int\\limits_{=\"\" {{{{y^2}}=\"\" 2}dy}=\"\" <br=\"\"><br>$$ = {1 \\over 4}\\left[ {{{{y^2}} \\over 2} + y} \\right]_{ - 1/2}^1\\,\\, - {1 \\over 2}\\left[ {{{{y^3}} \\over 3}} \\right]_{ - 1}^1$$\n<br><br>$$ = {1 \\over 4}\\left[ {{3 \\over 2} + {3 \\over 8}} \\right] - {9 \\over {48}}$$\n<br><br>$$ = {{15} \\over {32}} - {9 \\over {48}} = {{27} \\over {96}} = {9 \\over {32}}$$ ",
