        "chapterId": "area-under-the-curves",
        "title": "AIEEE 2010",
        "year": 2010,
        "difficulty": "Medium",
        "type": "SCQ",
        "question": "The area bounded by the curves $$y = \\cos x$$ and $$y = \\sin x$$ between the ordinates $$x=0$$ and $$x = {{3\\pi } \\over 2}$$ is ",
