        "question": "The sum of all real values of $$x$$ for which $$\\frac{3 x^{2}-9 x+17}{x^{2}+3 x+10}=\\frac{5 x^{2}-7 x+19}{3 x^{2}+5 x+12}$$ is equal to __________.",
