        "question": "Let $${S_1} = \\left\\{ {x \\in R - \\{ 1,2\\} :{{(x + 2)({x^2} + 3x + 5)} \\over { - 2 + 3x - {x^2}}} \\ge 0} \\right\\}$$ and $${S_2} = \\left\\{ {x \\in R:{3^{2x}} - {3^{x + 1}} - {3^{x + 2}} + 27 \\le 0} \\right\\}$$. Then, $${S_1} \\cup {S_2}$$ is equal to :",
