        "question": "Let $$S = \\left\\{ {x:x \\in \\mathbb{R}\\,\\mathrm{and}\\,{{(\\sqrt 3  + \\sqrt 2 )}^{{x^2} - 4}} + {{(\\sqrt 3  - \\sqrt 2 )}^{{x^2} - 4}} = 10} \\right\\}$$. Then $$n(S)$$ is equal to",
