        "question": "Let $\\mathbf{S}=\\left\\{x \\in \\mathbf{R}:(\\sqrt{3}+\\sqrt{2})^x+(\\sqrt{3}-\\sqrt{2})^x=10\\right\\}$. Then the number of elements in $\\mathrm{S}$ is :",
